---
const stats = [
  { target: 232, labelKey: "proof.registrations.label", label: "pre-registrations" },
  { target: 40, labelKey: "proof.installs.label", label: "installs" },
  { target: 2, labelKey: "proof.paying.label", label: "paying users" },
  { target: 61, labelKey: "proof.astraTools.label", label: "Astra tools" },
  { target: 79, labelKey: "proof.mcpTools.label", label: "MCP tools" },
];
---

<section id="proof" class="py-20 sm:py-24">
  <div class="page-container">
    <p class="t-eyebrow reveal" data-i18n="proof.eyebrow">Why Orbit</p>
    <h2 class="t-display reveal mt-3 max-w-[560px] [text-wrap:balance]" data-i18n="proof.title">
      Built by someone who needed it
    </h2>

    <dl
      class="reveal reveal-stagger mt-10 grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-8 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5"
    >
      {
        stats.map((stat) => (
          <div>
            <dd
              class="count-up font-display text-[40px] leading-none font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] text-fg-1 [font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums]"
              data-count-target={stat.target}
            >
              {stat.target}
            </dd>
            <dt class="t-secondary mt-2 text-fg-3" data-i18n={stat.labelKey}>
              {stat.label}
            </dt>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </dl>

    <figure
      class="reveal mt-12 rounded-[20px] bg-bg-card p-7 sm:p-9"
      style="box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px var(--color-hairline);"
    >
      <blockquote
        class="max-w-[62ch] font-sans text-[18px] leading-[1.6] text-fg-1 [text-wrap:pretty] sm:text-[20px]"
        data-i18n="proof.founder.body"
      >
        I'm a software engineer with ADHD. I ran my whole life out of Notion, but it grew so complex
        that keeping it up became its own chore. So I built Orbit: the simple, forgiving habit
        tracker I wished existed, for me and for anyone whose brain works the same way.
      </blockquote>
      <figcaption class="mt-5 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span
          class="flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full font-display text-[15px] font-bold text-fg-on-primary"
          style="background: var(--color-primary);"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          T
        </span>
        <span class="font-sans text-[14px] font-medium text-fg-2" data-i18n="proof.founder.name">
          Thomas, founder of Orbit
        </span>
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>
